      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior and interior show visible signs of wear and tear from regular use. While the car is operational, it may require some minor repairs or maintenance in the near future.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
